ActRoyal Canadian Mounted Police Act
PrecisAuthority to enter into an AGREEMENT RESPECTING BIOLOGY CASEWORK ANALYSIS with the Provinces of British Columbia, Alberta, Saskatchewan, Manitoba, New Brunswick, Nova Scotia, Prince Edward Island and Newfoundland and Labrador, and the Governments of Nunavut, Yukon and the Northwest Territories which provides for the sharing of costs associated with the forensic analysis of biological evidence arising out of criminal investigations.
